casebody.data:
Wednesday, February 24, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

99-127. State v. Adelman.

Summit App. No. 18824. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. On February 16, 1999, appellee filed a memorandum in response that exceeds the page limit prescribed by S.Ct.Prac.R. II(2)(B). Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the memorandum in response be, and hereby is, stricken.
